This is a list of the best SEO companies in the UK based on methodology, published results, and specialisation — not paid placements. As an independent SEO consultant, I have no financial relationship with any agency listed here. I am included on this list myself (transparently labelled), which means you can evaluate my approach alongside theirs and decide which fits your business.

Most "best SEO agency" lists charge £500-£5,000 for a featured spot. Every company on those lists paid to be there. This one does not work that way.

**Selection criteria:** verifiable case studies, publicly demonstrated methodology, client retention evidence, specialist depth or breadth of capability, and fit across different business types and budgets.

