## Blue Array — Best Specialist Agency for Pure SEO

**Based in:** Reading, Berkshire

[Blue Array](https://bluearray.co.uk) is one of the UK's specialist SEO agencies — meaning SEO is all they do, not one department among many. Based in Reading (locally relevant to this site), they have worked with large e-commerce and retail brands, and publish detailed SEO research through their blog. Specialist agencies typically provide more senior attention per pound spent than full-service agencies.

**Best for:** Mid-market to enterprise businesses wanting deep SEO expertise without paying for services they do not need. Strong fit for e-commerce, retail, and B2C businesses.

**Strengths:**
- Pure SEO focus means everyone in the company understands search
- Strong technical SEO capability demonstrated in published case studies
- Local to Reading and Berkshire — useful if you prefer in-person collaboration

**Considerations:**
- Less focus on content marketing and digital PR than some competitors
- Enterprise-level pricing for most engagements

