## Propellernet — Best for Ethical and Sustainable Brands

**Based in:** Brighton

[Propellernet](https://propellernet.co.uk) focuses on businesses whose values align with theirs — sustainability, purpose-driven brands, and companies with genuine stories to tell. They are an employee-owned agency with a strong culture, which tends to reduce staff turnover and improve client relationship quality. Their approach combines [content strategy](/services/content-briefs/) with link acquisition and technical SEO.

**Best for:** B-Corp certified businesses, sustainable brands, charities, and purpose-driven companies where authentic storytelling is central to marketing.

**Strengths:**
- Employee-owned model reduces the churn that damages client relationships at investor-backed agencies
- Strong editorial content capability
- Good cultural alignment for brands where ethics matter

**Considerations:**
