## What to Ask Any Agency Before Signing

Regardless of which company you approach, these questions separate genuinely capable providers from those that rely on sales process:

1. **"Show me Search Console data from a client in my industry."** Results that cannot be verified did not happen.
2. **"Who specifically will work on my account? Can I meet them?"** Senior pitch, junior delivery is standard at many agencies.
3. **"What deliverables do I own if we end the engagement after 3 months?"** You should own all strategy documents, audits, and content.
4. **"How has your methodology changed in the last 12 months?"** The SEO landscape changed substantially in 2024-2025. An agency that cannot answer this is not evolving.
5. **"What realistic results can I expect at 3 months, 6 months, and 12 months?"** Vague promises are a red flag. [How long SEO takes](/blog/how-long-does-seo-take/) gives you the benchmarks to evaluate any answer.

